{"tid":1777670,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你想停落黎，唔想再抗爭的話","createTime":"2019-12-10T11:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T11:31:07.000Z","uid":224916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0e82f31b403d0f1bf3201cb549ae68a88e1ff669","tid":1777670,"uid":224916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T11:22:59.000Z","msg":"你就諗返下由梁烈士起，到死第二個，死雙位數，死三位數，死兩千幾人，女手足俾人輪姦，男手足俾人壓住塊面磨地，係三四樓活生生比人掟落樓慘死，如果你諗完呢堆畫面，之後仍然諗住過返港豬生活，做個活死人，唔想再理咩抗爭，逆來順受，或者踩住人地屍體去享受生活嘅，fine，你唔好講出來，你偷生落去就得，你願意背住「無人性」生活落去就得。<br />\n<br />\n只係我做唔到。"},{"pid":"4b626ed7f73ba10a56cb80ad666eb0bd7843182d","tid":1777670,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T11:23:38.000Z","msg":"我會繼續努力架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（Twitter戰線）歐盟Magnitsky Act有重要進程<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776924</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">twitter要人: 歐盟今日啟動Magnitsky Act 立法程序，詳細議會仲要傾，但歐洲戰線開啟左啦，快啲入去講邊個國家的人最需要被裁裁啦！！</span><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n幫手入去retweet同推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入 －－》 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3capJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=14747ce5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"dfec2640124598aa2f7ab06f40b4f9a2dcffdb8b","tid":1777670,"uid":224916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T11:31:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj